cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper proposes a framework for change detection in scenes, which involves computer vision and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also incorporates object semantics, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper uses a dataset for evaluation, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves robotics applications, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics).
